ColumbiaCrimeReport is an Android application written in Java

--Current Version--
* Checks for police reports on the columbiasc.net website
* User can select the date the report was posted
* The application initiates a call to the website to pull down the app.

If you would like to contribute, see the wiki for details on potential features we'd like to add.  Screenshots are included.

